      "id": "PopularPost337362",
      "post_content": "@ DarthParallax   \nI agree with you. What's the porpouse to have characters like planeswalker when they don't do anything? What's the porpouse of having a villain like Nicol Bolas, when he lurks and cospirate but nothing happens? Beside the death of Mirron by Phyrexia (great story, by the way! And I like Phyrexia...), the only actual action we've seen are the fight between Liliana and Garruk in Avacyn Restored, in [Triumph of Ferocity](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Triumph of Ferocity) and [Triumph of Cruelty](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Triumph of Cruelty), but nothing more...   \n  \nThe storyboard done with the cards in Tempest was nice, but I understand why Wizards doesn't want to redo it, but nowaday we see no action between characters, and only a little about the interaction between planes, like during Kamigawa and Ravnica... I want more of these!",
      "posted_by": "leomistico",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost337362\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">@ DarthParallax <br/>I agree with you. What's the porpouse to have characters like planeswalker when they don't do anything? What's the porpouse of having a villain like Nicol Bolas, when he lurks and cospirate but nothing happens? Beside the death of Mirron by Phyrexia (great story, by the way! And I like Phyrexia...), the only actual action we've seen are the fight between Liliana and Garruk in Avacyn Restored, in <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Triumph of Ferocity\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Triumph of Ferocity\">Triumph of Ferocity</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Triumph of Cruelty\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Triumph of Cruelty\">Triumph of Cruelty</a>, but nothing more... <br/><br/>The storyboard done with the cards in Tempest was nice, but I understand why Wizards doesn't want to redo it, but nowaday we see no action between characters, and only a little about the interaction between planes, like during Kamigawa and Ravnica... I want more of these!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '337362'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy822\">leomistico</span>\r\n                                (9/2/