    {
      "id": "PopularPost319906",
      "post_content": "The new art actually looks like it's from a Space Colony, not Kamigawa....and yet I can see Kamigawa, kinda, in the Nezumi architecture. I LIKE this. It feels like it's from OLD School MAGIC, which felt twice as Sci-Fi and Philosophical as today's MAGIC story.   \n  \nI like MAGIC flavor, I LOVE Agents of Artifice, but even the very height of cool flavor Post-Mending holds nothing to the blaze of flavor that once was THE MULTIVERSE, in the time of Urza Planeswalker. Urza was the Obi-Wan Kenobi that held it all together and made it WORK. Magic used to be like....like Star Trek crossed with Star Wars crossed with Pastoral Symphony from Fantasia. Da da da DA dadada duh duh Duh DUH dadada....[Stormfront Pegasus](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stormfront Pegasus) anyone? :P [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt)? :P   \n  \nAh, forget about it.  \n  \n  \nThere are too many stories now. Too many Planeswalkers, but no Central Hero. If it's Jace, actually show some things happening to him. Actually get him to bring a New Coalition together against... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost319906\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">The new art actually looks like it's from a Space Colony, not Kamigawa....and yet I can see Kamigawa, kinda, in the Nezumi architecture. I LIKE this. It feels like it's from OLD School MAGIC, which felt twice as Sci-Fi and Philosophical as today's MAGIC story. <br/><br/>I like MAGIC flavor, I LOVE Agents of Artifice, but even the very height of cool flavor Post-Mending holds nothing to the blaze of flavor that once was THE MULTIVERSE, in the time of Urza Planeswalker. Urza was the Obi-Wan Kenobi that held it all together and made it WORK. Magic used to be like....like Star Trek crossed with Star Wars crossed with Pastoral Symphony from Fantasia. Da da da DA dadada duh duh Duh DUH dadada....<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stormfront Pegasus\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stormfront Pegasus\">Stormfront Pegasus</a> anyone? :P <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt\">Lightning Bolt</a>? :P <br/><br/>Ah, forget about it.<br/><br/><br/>There are too many stories now. Too many Planeswalkers, but no Central Hero. If it's Jace, actually show some things happening to him. Actually get him to bring a New Coalition together against... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 319906)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '319906'); return false;\">\r\n         